16
00:00:42,440 --> 00:00:45,760
and one fun part about the show is it's kind of pulled back the curtain.

17
00:00:45,760 --> 00:00:51,720
So at least in some sense, we got an idea of how ads and communication

18
00:00:51,720 --> 00:00:53,790
campaigns were built in the '60s.

