quickly online that said, "It's OK if ours bend"--

53
00:02:25,930 --> 00:02:29,010
poking fun at the notion of iPhones's product not working,

54
00:02:29,010 --> 00:02:32,160
but in a Kit Kat world, that's all good.

55
00:02:32,160 --> 00:02:32,920
Right?

56
00:02:32,920 --> 00:02:36,380
Perhaps one the most famous examples of real time marketing

57
00:02:36,380 --> 00:02:38,770
was in the Superbowl-- a couple of years back.

58
00:02:38,770 --> 00:02:39,400
Right?

59
